CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1945, pg. 18, reads: "Contest Winners - These youngsters were declared winners in baby contest sponsored recently at the Carney Post, on Duff Street: First Andrew Lee Dixon; second" Andrea Lark Williams; third, Joseph C. Carter (not shown). Others in photo are Diane Banks, Patricia Elaine Carter and Kathleen Joyce. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women holding babies and children, including Andrew Lee Dixon holding document, Andrea Lark Williams, Diane Banks, Patricia Elaine Carter, and Kathleen Joyce, posed in in front of flags for baby contest
